DBPL 99 - Call for papers
The Seventh International Workshop on Database Programming Languages will be held September 1 st to 4 th 1999 in Scotland , just before VLDB in Edinburgh .
Papers are sought on any subject related to the intersection between programming language and database research . In particular , DBPL welcomes papers on the interaction of theory and practice in this domain .
Submission deadline is 15 th March .
The co-chairs are Richard Connor ( University of Glasgow ) and Alberto Mendelzon ( University of Toronto ) .
The workshop will be held at Kinloch Rannoch , a remote location right in the heart of the Scottish highlands .
The workshop web site is at http : / / www . dcs . gla . ac . uk /
Feel free to direct any enquiries to dbpl 99 @ dcs . gla . ac . uk
Richard Connor Alberto Mendelzon
